X-WR-CALNAME:Weaver line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-21T04:30:00&endDate=2026-03-23T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Saturday 21 and Sunday 22 March\, no service between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Use VICTORIA LINE connections between Central London and Seven Sisters / Walthamstow Central. GREATER ANGLIA and STANSTED EXPRESS trains will not call at Hackney Downs and Seven Sisters. Replacement buses operate.
DTEND:20260323T012900Z
DTSTART:20260321T043000Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Planned Closure
UID:f1783569-562b-4505-8181-092c8678aab8@f178.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-28T04:30:00&endDate=2026-03-30T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Saturday 28 and Sunday 29 March\, no service between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Use VICTORIA LINE connections between Central London and Seven Sisters / Walthamstow Central. GREATER ANGLIA and STANSTED EXPRESS trains will not call at Hackney Downs and Seven Sisters. Replacement buses operate.
