BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-03-19T22:45:00&endDate=2026-03-20T01:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Monday 16\, Tuesday 17 and Thursday 19 March\, after 2245 each evening\, no service between Hackney Downs and Enfield Town / Cheshunt. Last through trains operate at 2245 from Liverpool Street to Cheshunt (except on Wednesday when it is at 2215)\, 2253 from Enfield Town to Liverpool Street\, 2300 from Liverpool Street to Enfield Town and 2302 from Cheshunt to Liverpool Street. Use Clapton for Rectory Road and Stoke Newington\, and local London Buses services for Stamford Hill. Replacement buses operate. The limited number of southbound GREATER ANGLIA and STANSTED EXPRESS trains after midnight which usually call at Seven Sisters are diverted via Tottenham Hale instead
DTEND:20260320T012900Z
DTSTART:20260319T224500Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Part Closure
UID:4a9b18ec-569b-4139-a420-07bc32ba0ae1@4a9b.org
END:VEVENT
